experience.title: Support & Network Services Intern

experience.title: Information Technology Student Center Intern
experience.description: Resolved student center questions and arranged peer-to-peer tutoring/assistance with specific students in CSS program; prepared and delivered a Microsoft Office training session and training videos for the general public in a workforce environment; created and enabled multiple custom virtual machines in a sandboxed environment to distinguish networking and connectivity; continued research and interacted with Microsoft Windows, Macintosh OS X, mobile, and Linux operating systems.
